               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph ID="ID36">Acyclovir Ointment USP, 5% is supplied as a white to off-white color ointment. Each gram of acyclovir ointment USP, 5% contains 50 mg acyclovir, USP in a polyethylene glycol base. </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>It is supplied as follows: </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>5-g tubes         NDC 62332-248-05</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>15-g tubes       NDC 62332-248-15</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>30-g tubes       NDC 62332-248-30</paragraph>
                  <paragraph> </paragraph>
                  <paragraph> <content styleCode="bold">Store at 15° to 25°C (59° to 77°F). [See USP Controlled Room Temperature]. Store in a dry place</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold"> </content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Call your doctor for medical advice about side effects. You may report side effects to FDA at 1-800-FDA-1088.</paragraph>
